                                        <div class="rs-program-details-about">
                                            <h3 class="section-title text has-theme-blue mb-15">About Course</h3>

                                            <p class="rs-program-details-desc">
                                                D.M.L.T. graduates play a key role in healthcare by performing accurate
                                                diagnostic tests that support clinical decision-making. The course
                                                covers laboratory management, quality control, and modern testing
                                                technologies, equipping students for careers in hospitals, diagnostic
                                                labs, and research institutions.
                                            </p>
                                        </div>
                                        <div class="rs-program-details-about-wrapper">
                                            <div class="row g-5">
                                                <div class="col-xl-8 col-lg-8">
                                                    <div class="rs-program-details-about-content mt-30">
                                                        <h5 class="rs-program-details-title text-blue">
                                                            Diploma in Medical Laboratory Technology Program
                                                        </h5>

                                                        <h6 class="rs-program-details-title text-blue mt-20 mb-20">
                                                            Session: 2025 - 2026
                                                        </h6>

                                                        <h6 class="rs-program-details-title text-blue">
                                                            Course Structure
                                                        </h6>

                                                        <p class="rs-program-details-about-desc mt-20">
                                                            The curriculum builds comprehensive laboratory competence
                                                            through classroom learning, hands-on practicals, and
                                                            supervised clinical postings in diagnostic laboratories.
                                                        </p>
                                                        <ul class="rs-program-details-about-list">
                                                            <li><span>Duration:</span> 2 Years</li>
                                                            <li><span>Eligibility:</span> 10+2 (Science Preferred)</li>
                                                            <li><span>Training:</span> Practical & Clinical Laboratory
                                                                Exposure
                                                            </li>
                                                            <li><span>Career Scope:</span> Hospitals, Diagnostic Labs &
                                                                Research Institutions</li>
                                                        </ul>
                                                        <div class="curriculum-wrapper">
                                                            <h6 class="curriculum-sec-title">
                                                                Core Learning Areas
                                                            </h6>

                                                            <div class="curriculum-item-wrapper">

                                                                <div class="curriculum-item">
                                                                    <h6 class="curriculum-title">Clinical Hematology
                                                                    </h6>
                                                                    <p class="curriculum-content">
                                                                        Study of blood components, counts, and related
                                                                        disorders.
                                                                    </p>
                                                                </div>

                                                                <div class="curriculum-item">
                                                                    <h6 class="curriculum-title">Clinical Biochemistry
                                                                    </h6>
                                                                    <p class="curriculum-content">
                                                                        Testing of biochemical parameters relevant to
                                                                        diagnosis.
                                                                    </p>
                                                                </div>

                                                                <div class="curriculum-item">
                                                                    <h6 class="curriculum-title">Microbiology</h6>
                                                                    <p class="curriculum-content">
                                                                        Identification of pathogens through culture and
                                                                        staining techniques.
                                                                    </p>
                                                                </div>

                                                                <div class="curriculum-item">
                                                                    <h6 class="curriculum-title">Histopathology Basics
                                                                    </h6>
                                                                    <p class="curriculum-content">
                                                                        Introduction to tissue processing and basic
                                                                        pathology.
                                                                    </p>
                                                                </div>

                                                                <div class="curriculum-item">
                                                                    <h6 class="curriculum-title">Laboratory Quality
                                                                        Control</h6>
                                                                    <p class="curriculum-content">
                                                                        Maintaining accuracy and standards in laboratory
                                                                        testing.
                                                                    </p>
                                                                </div>

                                                            </div>
